             was indicted for <rs id="t18080113-3-off12" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18080113-3-off12" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18080113-3-off12" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18080113-3-cd13" type="crimeDate">18th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080113-3-off12 t18080113-3-cd13"></join>, a gown, value 12 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18080113-3-victim63" type="victimName">
                           William 
                           Ward
                        <interp inst="t18080113-3-victim63" type="surname" value="Ward"></interp>
